### 4.2 Alur Proses Absensi

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 Anggota
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant FaceAPI as 🤖 face-api.js
    participant GeoAPI as 📍 Geolocation API
    participant Server as 🖧 Laravel Server
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database

    User->>Browser: Buka halaman absensi
    Browser->>GeoAPI: Minta izin lokasi
    GeoAPI-->>Browser: Koordinat (lat, lng)
    
    Browser->>Server: Kirim koordinat untuk validasi
    Server->>DB: Ambil lokasi absensi terdekat
    
    alt Jarak > 30 meter
        Server-->>Browser: ❌ Ditolak - Di luar radius
        Browser-->>User: Tampilkan pesan error + peta
    else Jarak ≤ 30 meter
        Server-->>Browser: ✅ Lokasi valid
        Browser->>Browser: Aktifkan kamera
        Browser->>FaceAPI: Load model face detection
        FaceAPI->>FaceAPI: Deteksi wajah dari kamera
        
        alt Wajah tidak terdeteksi
            FaceAPI-->>Browser: ❌ Wajah tidak ditemukan
            Browser-->>User: Tampilkan pesan error
        else Wajah terdeteksi
            FaceAPI->>FaceAPI: Generate face descriptor (128-dim vector)
            Browser->>Server: Kirim face descriptor + foto + koordinat
            Server->>DB: Ambil face descriptor tersimpan milik user
            Server->>Server: Hitung Euclidean Distance
            
            alt Distance > threshold (0.6)
                Server-->>Browser: ❌ Wajah tidak cocok
                Browser-->>User: Tampilkan pesan error
            else Distance ≤ threshold (0.6)
                Server->>DB: Simpan record absensi
                Server-->>Browser: ✅ Absensi berhasil
                Browser-->>User: Tampilkan konfirmasi sukses
            end
        end
    end
```

