## 10. Keamanan

| Aspek | Implementasi |
|---|---|
| **Authentication** | Laravel Breeze + session-based auth |
| **Authorization** | Role middleware + Laravel Policies |
| **CSRF** | Token CSRF di setiap form |
| **Face Data** | Descriptor disimpan di server, bukan di client |
| **GPS Spoofing** | Validasi server-side + timestamp check |
| **Rate Limiting** | Throttle absensi (max 1x per jadwal) |
| **File Upload** | Validasi tipe & ukuran foto |
| **XSS** | Blade auto-escaping |
| **SQL Injection** | Eloquent ORM parameterized queries |

> [!WARNING]
> **Anti-spoofing GPS**: Meskipun GPS bisa di-spoof di perangkat rooted/jailbroken, kombinasi dengan face recognition memberikan lapisan keamanan tambahan. Untuk keamanan ekstra, bisa ditambahkan pengecekan apakah mock location diaktifkan (khusus Android via User-Agent detection).

